➜美人鱼“游”进古墓里，今晚听《故事》为你娓娓道来
http://www.sohu.com/a/414270870_170190	14400
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200821/c1bc6902495843978b692169c9ce2189.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=210929706&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 2016年4月，宁夏彭阳县罗洼乡张湾村的村民在修整农田时，发现一座古墓，经专家推断，这是一座宋金时期的古墓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/973c7bc00bfc4a37bef474f9f9e81f66.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">令人感到惊奇的是，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墓室中的砖墙上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有着美人鱼造型的砖雕。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200821/86cbfe5dd46f4ce883cf18c85857ee8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">更为神奇的是，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在墓室中的两处美人鱼造型，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一处从面貌上来看，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她是一位年轻女子；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200821/f069f6dfd7104b65af9499604dfb2143.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而另外一副砖雕，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">线条硬朗，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从头饰、上身、鱼尾等部位看，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他更像是一位男士。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200821/aab10a58d8de47099b78ecfcc77f4d50.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">①</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">西北偏远山区古墓中，为何会有美人鱼造型砖雕？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/1f45911fe83e4a3d89dd3b3175afaa3f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>②</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">两处人鱼造型为何还分男女？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200821/a64905344f104c0a9fbe2feeca676d69.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">③</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">墓主人的身份究竟为何人？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200821/31f1df769a7046b697c61e5892923124.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">④</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了美人鱼，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墓中的其他砖雕的造型又会是什么样？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200821/b7bde99481d2415baf8bada98d8cc8e8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200821/4ed355f149e048ccbbc46f70374c618e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">种种疑问，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宁夏彭阳县博物馆副馆长杨彦斌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">带你走进古墓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">8月22日21:58，宁夏卫视</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">且听《故事》，娓娓道来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200821/0c388438ec2847caa9b9b900fc135873.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
